python 语法
-------------------------
语句  角色 例子
赋值@创建引用@a,b,c = 'good', 'bad','ok'
调用@执行函数@log.write("spam, ham")
打印调用@打印对象@print 'Killer is joke'
if/else/else@选择动作@if "python" in text: print text
for/else@序列迭代@for x in mylist: print x
while/else@一般循环@while X > Y: print 'Hello'
pass@空占位符@while True: pass
break@退出循环@while True: if exittest(): break
continue@循环继续@while True: if skiptest(): continue
def@函数和方法@def f(a, b, c=1, *d): print(a+b+c+d[0])
return@函数结果@def f(a, b, c=1, *d): print(a+b+c+d[0])
yield@生成器函数@def gen(n):for i in n:yield i*2
global@命名空间@x = 'old'\ndef function():global x,y; x = 'new'
nonlocal@命名空间(3.0)@def outer():x='old'\ndef function():nonlocal x; x = 'new'
import@模块访问@import sys
from@属性访问@from sys import stdin
class@创建对象@class Subclass(Supperclass): def method(self): pass
try/except/finally@捕捉异常@try:action():except:print 'action error'
raise@触发异常@raise EndSearch(location)
assert@调试检查@assert X>Y, 'X too small'
with/as@环境管理器@with open('data') as my file:process(myfile)
del@删除引用@del data[k]\ndel data[i:j]\ndel obj.attr\ndel variable
